Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Literary papyrus
Description: Literary papyrus with two vertical columns of letters: on the left a series of isolated omikron letters, on the right sequences starting with omikron. The same remarks are valid as on the entry for P. Lille 110 (a) verso on the handwriting (childish or adult?). Both exercises are by the same author.
